---
title: Caribbean Salmon & Mango Salsa with Coconut Corn Rice & Baby Broccoli
description: It’s time to put your feet up, sit back and relax, preferably on a sunny beach with a chilled beverage because this bowl is ready for summer time vibes. Fresh Caribbean salmon with a fruitful mango salsa on top with a sunny yet mild chilli sauce to kick start the relaxation.
